12) Why This Geometry Works

Scale-free networks have three properties useful here:
	1.	Resilience
Local failures don’t collapse the system.
	2.	Rapid innovation
Small markets can experiment independently.
	3.	Discovery amplification
The bazaar exposes unexpected combinations.

